{
  "texts": [
    "Notice that our prompt template instructs ChatGPT to report the hazards in a list form and place a colon after each topic name is introduced, thus allowing the API to extract all topics accurately and automatically from each response 16.",
    "Regarding parameters that might affect ChatGPT's outputs, we used all default settings, including that for temperature (randomness of responses) and max_tokens (response length).",
    "Responses per country took approximately 30 seconds to retrieve, on average.",
    "This table reports the results of GPT-4's first iteration.",
    "True positives (TP) occur when both GPT-4 and validation data identify the theme as a vulnerability for the given country, whereas true negatives (TN) occur when both sources do not claim a theme as an issue for the selected country."
  ]
}